I made this localization pack by doing the following:

nibtool -L English.lproj/MainMenu.nib > English.lproj/MainMenu.strings
mkdir LocalizationPack
mkdir LocalizationPack/WinHex1.0b2LocalizationPack
svn export --non-interactive English.lproj \
LocalizationPack/WinHex1.0b2Localization/English.lproj
rm -r Localizationpack/WinHex1.0b2LocalizationPack/English.lproj MainMenu.nib

Then I zipped it up in the Finder to produce:
WinHex1.0b2LocalizationPack.zip
